<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-16711] Split ViewComplexTest to avoid timeouts after being moved away from &apos;long&apos; junits</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16711</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Under &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16670&quot; title=&quot;Flaky ViewComplexTest, ViewFilteringTest and InsertUpdateIfConditionTest&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-16670&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-16670&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; we decided to move some tickets from the &apos;long&apos; junit section to the std one. This required splitting them to avoid timing out but ViewComplexTest needs further splitting.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13382054">CASSANDRA-16711</key>
            <summary>Split ViewComplexTest to avoid timeouts after being moved away from &apos;long&apos; junits</summary>
